node.text: Camp Honeyside is a virtual summer camp brought to you by #HONEYMAID - In this post, Simone and I will make Peanut Butter Bumblebees and do a fun, easy crafting project - Flower + Leaf-Pressed Tablemats. #honeymaid @honeymaidsnacks #ad

node.text: Hello old friend.... did anyone else have this “Sir Swatch”Swatch in 1986? It was always my favorite. I got one when I was Simone’s age and I’m so happy @swatch re-released it! Wearing it feels like an old friend coming home for a visit! #swatch (just fun. Not an ad!)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Scout Masterson on March 15, 2021 tagging @glamourous1.

node.text: Finally today. I was eligible for a vaccine. After a year of hiding from the world beyond our house. It was amazing to take that 1st shot. I cried. Not because of the needle. I cried because I was so excited to know that soon I’ll be protected. As protected as I can be. I got the vaccine, not only for me, but for all of these beautiful people in the following pictures. Thx to my friend @glamourous1 for finding me an appointment on day 1. XOXO. (NOTE: Comments that say the vaccine is a hoax. Or coronavirus doesn’t exist will be DELETED.)

node.text: Rare outing this morning out of the house to celebrate @thebillhorn and @tiffanithiessen birthdays with the most amazing breakfast sandwiches from @calabama in Hollywood. She delivers the sandwiches to you in a bucket from her top floor apartment- and they are THE BEST! THX @tiffanithiessen for the deliciousness!! #calabama
